NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 12, 2010
Jonas Jerebko
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   


   JONAS JEREBKO: It's an honor to be a rookie on the team and to be European, too. I'm very honored.  
  
  Q. Did you know some of your teammates coming in or are you trying to get to know the guys?  
 JONAS JEREBKO: I know of them and I know them a little bit. It'll be fun to play the game and see everybody have a good time.  
  
  Q. What are your thoughts on getting to play for a Hall of Fame coach? It's got to be an honor?  
 JONAS JEREBKO: Of course. You look at all the veterans and all the good players around you and just take whatever you can get.   
  
  Q. (Inaudible).   
 JONAS JEREBKO: Exactly, seven straight years, and we want to make it eight.   
   
